Description:
This test is to verify the functionality of the NIC "Bonding" function.
 
Preconditions:
  1. Install OS (Linux OS)
  2. Install NIC driver
  3. Connect two of SUT1’s OB NIC ports to a switch of the appropriate (max capable) speed
  4. Connect one of SUT2’s OB NIC ports to the switch referenced.
